name: WEST COAST SHUTTLE - AMERICAN EAGLE FIRST CLASS, SJC-LAX, EMBRAER 170
description:
In this video, we take a short, 50-minute flight between California's tech capital, San Jose, and Los Angeles International Airport. 

A fine summer day, and some lovely views of coastal California and Los Padres Forest. 

Enjoy!
